---
import CaseStudyLayout from "../layouts/CaseStudyLayout.astro";
---

<CaseStudyLayout
  title="Sparks Grove — Delta Air Lines"
  description="How I led design for the Delta News Hub — a unified communications platform for the world's most-traveled airline, serving 90,000 employees and millions of customers."
  ogImage="/images/sparks-grove/news-hub.jpg"
>
  <style>
    :root {
      --navy: #0b1b2b;
      --delta-red: #c8102e;
      --warm-white: #f7f5f2;
      --text-primary: #1a1a1a;
      --text-secondary: #5a5a5a;
      --text-light: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
      --accent: #c8102e;
    }

    /* ── Hero (full-bleed photo) ── */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      height: 90vh;
      min-height: 800px;
      overflow: hidden;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 120px 40px;
    }

    .hero-bg {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .hero-bg img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center 25%;
    }

    /* Global Overlay Scrim - The Middle Ground */
    .hero-bg::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: rgba(11, 27, 43, 0.55);
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      padding: 0 40px;
      max-width: 900px;
    }

    .hero-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
      font-size: clamp(48px, 6vw, 84px);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: #fff;
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: #fff;
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }

    /* ── Showcase ── */
    .showcase {
      background: var(--navy);
      padding: 160px 80px;
    }

    .showcase .section-heading {
      color: #fff;
    }
    .showcase .section-body {
      color: var(--text-light);
    }

    .showcase-grid {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 80px;
      margin-top: 80px;
      max-width: 1300px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .showcase-item {
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1);
    }

    .showcase-item img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    .showcase-caption {
      padding: 40px 48px;
    }

    .showcase-caption h3 {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .showcase-caption p {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── Two-up layout ── */
    .two-up {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 64px;
    }

    /* ── Event Section ── */
    .event-section {
      background: #080d14;
      padding: 160px 80px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 0.7fr;
      gap: 120px;
      align-items: center;
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .event-text .section-heading {
      color: #fff;
    }
    .event-text .section-body {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    }

    /* ── Full Bleed Image ── */
    .full-bleed-closing {
      height: 70vh;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .full-bleed-closing img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    /* ── Responsive ── */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .hero {
        min-height: 600px;
        padding: 120px 24px 80px;
      }
      .hero-content {
        padding: 0;
      }
      .showcase {
        padding: 100px 32px;
      }
      .showcase-grid {
        gap: 48px;
      }
      .event-section {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        padding: 100px 32px;
        gap: 64px;
      }
      .two-up {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 48px;
      }
    }
  </style>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg">
      <img
        src="/images/sparks-grove/delta-777-right-inflight_new_livery.jpg"
        alt="Delta 777 in flight"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-label">Case Study &mdash; Delta Air Lines</div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">High-Fidelity Storytelling for an Iconic Brand</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        Leading the design team that unified Delta's digital newsroom, serving
        90,000 employees and millions of passengers annually.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Context -->
  <section class="context">
    <div class="context-inner">
      <div>
        <div class="section-label">The Challenge</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">
          Elevating corporate communications to match the in-flight experience.
        </h2>
        <p class="section-body">
          As UX Practice Leader for Sparks Grove (North Highland's innovation
          agency), I led the strategic consulting engagement for the Delta News
          Hub. Delta's internal and external communications lived across
          fragmented legacy systems. I directed our agency teams to architect a
          unified platform serving corporate comms, media relations, and 90,000
          employees under one cohesive, premium experience.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="meta-grid">
          <div class="meta-item">
            <h4>My Role</h4>
            <p>UX Design Practice Leader</p>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <h4>Agency</h4>
            <p>Sparks Grove &mdash; North Highland</p>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <h4>Scope</h4>
            <p>Practice Leadership, Strategic Consulting</p>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <h4>Impact</h4>
            <p>Secured $3M+ client engagement</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Showcase -->
  <div class="showcase">
    <div class="section-label">The Work</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">Delta News Hub Leadership</h2>
    <p class="section-body">
      I led the agency's multidisciplinary product and design teams in
      establishing a content-rich platform that balanced editorial storytelling
      with real-time operational priorities.
    </p>

    <div class="showcase-grid">
      <div class="showcase-item">
        <img src="/images/sparks-grove/news-hub.jpg" alt="News Hub Desktop" />
        <div class="showcase-caption">
          <h3>Editorial Architecture</h3>
          <p>
            Directed the strategy for a modular, category-driven framework
            designed to scale globally.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="two-up">
        <div class="showcase-item">
          <img src="/images/sparks-grove/DNH01.jpg" alt="IA & Header" />
          <div class="showcase-caption">
            <h3>Information Strategy</h3>
            <p>
              Oversaw the IA development, prioritizing real-time audience needs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="showcase-item">
          <img src="/images/sparks-grove/delta-4.jpg" alt="Mobile Views" />
          <div class="showcase-caption">
            <h3>Design Oversight</h3>
            <p>
              Managed the visual execution to ensure editorial quality was
              maintained across all touchpoints.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Agency Leadership -->
  <div class="event-section">
    <div class="event-image">
      <img
        src="/images/sparks-grove/gala_5.jpg"
        alt="Human Experience Design"
        style="filter: grayscale(100%) contrast(1.1);"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="event-text">
      <div class="section-label">Practice Leadership</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Transforming the agency.</h2>
      <p class="section-body">
        The Delta engagement represented just one key aspect of my purview. As
        Practice Leader, I transformed the agency itself from a traditional
        waterfall model to agile software development and lean product
        management, repositioning the entire practice around "Human Experience
        Design" (HxD). Over 2.5 years, I pitched and won $4.7M+ in new business
        and provided product methodology coaching for executives at major
        Fortune 500s, including The Home Depot. This transformation earned the
        National Impact Award in 2016.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Closing -->
  <section class="full-bleed-closing">
    <img
      src="/images/sparks-grove/20150925_a330a2a_stills_cam1-1179-v2.jpg.jpeg"
      alt="A330 Inflight"
    />
  </section>
</CaseStudyLayout>
